<h2>Purpose</h2>
<p>
  Grounds decision
  <a href="/backlog/1866-backlog-prioritisation-summary-pill-conversion-to-we-filter-/">#1866</a> — converting
  the <code>/backlog/</code> Prioritisation pills to FUI <code>we-filter-chip</code> under dogfood epic
  <a href="/backlog/777-dogfood-the-we-docs-website-on-fui-components-rework-the-sit/">#777</a> (blocks
